transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Thank you for calling Viagra, I can help you today.

Speaker 2: Hi, my name is John Schumacher and I keep getting these things in the mail and charged by ScoreBlue and I don't want them.

Speaker 1: So I could take another prescription.

Speaker 2: What's that?

Speaker 1: I could take a look into your prescription, what's your zip code?

Speaker 2: Did you ask me a question?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I just asked you if I could take a look into your prescription, what's your zip code?

Speaker 2: Oh yeah, you want my prescription number?

Speaker 1: Sir, I asked for your zip code.

Speaker 2: Oh, 92064.

Speaker 1: Last name?

Speaker 2: Schumacher.

Speaker 1: You want spelling?

Speaker 2: What's your first name?

Speaker 1: John.

Speaker 2: Okay, I pulled you up in my system here.

Speaker 1: So I see you're currently set up for the VIP service for the AGU Viagra.

Speaker 2: Did you want to make any changes or delay any orders?

Speaker 1: Yeah, I want to cancel all the orders you've sent me.

Speaker 2: We can cancel any future orders.

Speaker 1: Can't cancel what you've already received, but I can go ahead and do that for you.

Speaker 2: Yeah, and take out the subscribe part.

Speaker 1: And, you know, the other thing was the first order that I sent out, I called,

Speaker 2: and it said I could get my money back.

Speaker 1: And I did.

Speaker 2: So I saved some, but I called in, and she says, oh, you need some activation stuff.

Speaker 1: So I ate that, and it didn't do any good.

Speaker 2: These Silvanafils just don't work for me.

Speaker 1: So she said I could get my money back.

Speaker 2: I'd like to get that plus whatever you've sent me.

Speaker 1: Yeah, so you need to return whatever you have to the address that's on the bottle.

Speaker 2: Once it gets there, they're going to issue you a refund.

Speaker 1: I tried.

Speaker 2: I put the sender on it, and they stuck it back in my inbox.

Speaker 1: I can go ahead and give you return instructions so that way you can better understand how to send these back.

Speaker 2: But once they arrive to our pharmacy, they'll go ahead and give you a refund.

Speaker 1: So you need to return them.

Speaker 2: Okay, so are you going to email me instructions on how to return them?

Speaker 1: Our support team is going to just email you the return instructions.

Speaker 2: Yeah.

Speaker 1: You'll be able to get instructions on how to return this.

Speaker 2: Yeah, that would be great.

Speaker 1: Perfect. You're all set.

Speaker 2: I hope you have a good day now.

Speaker 1: Bye-bye.
